OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry day with some
OL,6,Flong sunny spells. Turning cloudier
OL,7,Fthrough the afternoon but still some
OL,8,Fhazy sunny spells. Light winds in the
OL,9,Fmorning but turning a little breezier
OL,10,Flater.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry and mostly cloudy start
OL,13,Fthen rain spreading eastwards through
OL,14,Fthe evening. Cloudy with outbreaks of
OL,15,Frain overnight, becoming drier with
OL,16,Fclear spells towards dawn. Winds
OL,17,Fbecoming strong.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
