OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA mixed day with some bright
OL,6,Fand sunny spells but also blustery
OL,7,Fshowers feeding in from the west,
OL,8,Fshowers perhaps wintry at times. Best
OL,9,Fof the sunny spells in east.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FSunny
OL,12,Fspells and showers early Saturday,
OL,13,Fthen rain and strong winds spreading
OL,14,Fnorth later, risk of gales. Blustery
OL,15,Fshowers with gale risk easing on
OL,16,FSunday. Dry with sunny spells Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
